<sect1 id="template-intro">
<title
>Ukwazisa kwi Templates</title>

<para
>KULUNGILE, ngoko umbuzo wokuqala onokuba nawo yi:</para>

<para
><emphasis
>Kutheni kufuneka ndisebenzise izakhelo ezisekwe kumqhubekekisi wegama, xa ndivuya kakhulu ukubhala iileta zam kweyangoku, ubeko lwephepha, umqhubekisi wegama? </emphasis
></para>

<para
>Ngoku iindaba ezimnandi zezi, ukunyenyisa kwizakhelo ezisekwe kumqhubekekisi wegama kulula kwaye xa ukhetha itemplate, &kword; ingasebenza njengobeko lwephepha lomqhubekekisi wegama omqhelileyo. Kukho itemplates ezikhoyo kuhambelwano olucacileyo nosebenziso losuku nosuku.</para>

<para
>Xa ufuna ukujikelezisa uxwebhu olunzima kakhulu (iileta zendaba, amaphepha aplagwayo, &etc;), ngoko ke, uzakufuna ukuswitsha kwisicelo esahlukileyo ukujikelezisa la maxwebhu athile. Kukho itemplates kwi &kword; ezizakukunceda ukujikelezisa iileta zendaba okanye amanye anzima kakhulu amaxwebhu.</para>

<para
>KULUNGILE. Ngoko ngoku ukuba ufuna ukunika oku uzamo, sizakuthetha ngokufutshane malunga nokuba zintoni itemplates, zingakwenzela ntoni itemplates kwaye usebenza njani ngetemplates.</para>

<para
><emphasis
>Yintoni itemplates kwaye zingandenzela ntoni</emphasis
></para>

<para
>Itemplate kungacingwa ukuba iyimold equtshiweyo yoxwebhu lakho.</para>

<para
>Xa sihlala phantsi ukubhala uxwebhu, sele sinengcamango yokuba izakujongeka njani imveliso yokugqibela. Ukuba ubhala ileta kwishishini, ufuna uxwebhu elinomhlathi omnye, elihamba yonke indawo ngapha kwephepha, kwaye ukusuka phezulu ukuya ezantsi kwephepha. Xa uhlala phantsi ukubhala ileta yendaba yeqela lobulali, ngoko ke, ungafuna iwonga elikhulu ngapha ngentla, nemihlathi emininzi yemiba ekhawulezayo yendaba.</para>

<para
>Nge &kword;, ungasebenzisa le ngcamango igqitywe phambili yendlela olwakho uxwebhu luzakujongeka ngayo ukwenza umsebenzi wakho lula. Ngokusebenzisa itemplate, ongenza kuyo iqela lezakhelo ukusondeza olu beko lokugqibela. Lweleta yakho yeshishini, ungakhetha isakhelo esinye esikhulu esigquma iphepha phezulu ukuya ezantsi nakwicala ngecala (ngaphandlekwemida kunjalo). Yalo leta yendaba, ngoko ke, ungagqiba ukuba emibini okanye emithathu imihlathi yoxwebhu ingaphezulu kokuthandayo. Xa ukhetha le template, &kword; kuzakukwenzela izakhelo.</para>

<para
><emphasis
>Ukuba ndigqibe mva ukutshintsha ubeko lwam</emphasis
></para>

<para
>Oku akuyongxaki. Ukuba uqala uxwebhu lakho njengomhalthi owodwa kwaye ugqiba mva ukuba imihlathi emibini ingcono kwiimfuno zakho, ungadibanisa omnye umhlathi. Injongo zetemplates ayikokunqamla umsebenzi wakho ukutshintsha ubeko lwakho, kodwa kungcono ukuthatha omnye wolayisho lomsebenzi ngaphandle xa kusenzeka. Ukukhetha eyiyo itemplate xa uqala uxwebhu lakho kuzakucacisa ufomato (njengoko kuchasiwe kukhetho oko itemplate yokungagqibekanga nokwenza olwakho utshintsho mva.), kodwa ibalulekile kwakhona ukukhumbula ukuba ukukhetha itemplate engeyiyo akuzukunqanda umsebenzi wakho.</para>

<para
><emphasis
>Usebenza ngezakhelo (aka Uxwebhu Lakho Lokuqala)</emphasis
></para>

<para
>Icandelo elilandelayo, liqulathe izihloko ezimbini zesakhelo omele uziqonde phambi kokuba siqhubekeke, ilandelwa linqwanqwa nge nqwanqwa ngapha kwemisebenzi ebaluleke kakhulu ozakufuna ukuziqonda ukugqiba uxwebhu olunzima. Sizakujikelezisa isiqalo seleta yendaba usebenzisa olu fundiso. Ukuba awufuni ukugqiba ufindiso, okanye unemibuzo malunga neziphumo ezithile zezakhelo, ungasebenzisa okulandelayo ukuxhuma ngqo kwelo candelo lofundiso.</para>

