<sect1 id="wp-vs-dtp">
<title
>Umahluko phakathi kokubhaliweyo okuhlenga-hlengisiweyo netemplates Zobeko Lwephepha</title>

<para
>Phambi kokuqala ngofundiso, kubalulekile ukuba umahluko phakathi kokuhlenga-hlengisiweyo okubhaliweyo netemplates zobeko lwephepha zicacile engqondweni yakho.</para>

<variablelist
> <varlistentry
> <term
>Okubhaliweyo kuhlenga-hlengisiwe</term
> <listitem
> <para
>Itemplates zokubhaliweyo okuhlenga-hlengisiweyo ziyilelwe ukusebenza njengabaqhubekisi begama bohlenga-hlengiso lwephepha. Xa ukhetha itemplate yokubhaliweyo okuhlenga-hlengisiweyo, uzakwenzxa itemplate ngesinye okanye ngaphezulu izakhelo. Isakhelo sokuqala siqhotyoshelwe kubungakanani bephepha lexwebhu lakho. Xa unyusa okanye uhlisa ubungakanani bephepha okanye utshintsha imida, ubungakanani besakhelo bunyenyiswa ngokuzenzekelayo. Uyi <emphasis
>hayi</emphasis
> ekwazi ukusa esi sakhelo jikelele kwiphepha kwaye awunakucima esi sakhelo. Ukuba ufuna ukunyenyisa ubungakanani okanye indawo yesi sakhelo, kufuneka <link linkend="page-format"
>nyenyisa imida</link
>. Phezu kwesakhelo sokuqala, unga, kunjalo, dibanisa izakhelo ezongezelelweyo. Ezi zakhelo zingaqulatha imifanekiso, okubhaliweyo okanye nayiphi na into oyifunayo. Ezi zakhelo zintsha zingasiwa, zilinganiselwe-kwakhona kwaye zicinywe ukulungelana neemfuno zakho. Ukuba uyayifuna, &kword; izakusonga okubhaliweyo kwisakhelo sokuqala jikelele kulo naluphi ulwazi kuzo naziphi izakhelo ezilandelanayo.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
>Ubeko lwephepha</term
> <listitem
> <para
>Ezi templates ziyilelwe upapasho lwe desktop. Xa ukhetha itemplate kolu hlobo, zonke izakhelo zenziwa ngokulinganayo. Oku kulapho umahluko phakathi kobeko lwephepha nokubhaliweyo okuhlenga-hlengisiweyo kulele khona. Akukho nanye kwizakhelo kwi template yobeko lwephepha ebotshelelwe kwiphepha ngokuqinileyo njengesakhelo esingundoqo kwitemplate yokubhaliweyo okuhlenga-hlengisiweyo enjalo. Isakhelo ngasinye sizimele kubungakanani bephepha, kwaye inga siwa okanye yenziwe ubungakanani-kwakhona ngaphandle kokutshintsha imida, &etc; Kunjalo oku kuthetha ukuba ukulungisa imida okanye ubungakanani bephepha loxwebhu lakho kufuna ukuba usa/uyayilinganisela kwakhona ngobunye isakhelo ngasinye. </para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> </variablelist>

<para
>Njengoko ubona, ukhetho phakathi kobeko lwephepha ne templates ezihlenga-hlengisiweyo zokubhaliweyo lukhetho phakathi kogobeko (Ubeko Lwephepha) no ncedo (Okubhaliweyo okuhlenga-hlengiosiweyo). Ungenza naluphi na uxwebhu oluthandayo ngodidi lwetemplate.</para>

<para
>Ukuba umba we templates awukacaci, nceda landela ngofundiso olulandelayo. Uxwebhu lokuqala olwenzayo luzakusebenzisa itemplate Yobeko Lwephepha. Oku kuzakunceda ucacise ngqo indlela itemplates zisebenza ngayo.</para
